      <p>These deposit conditions set out the terms on which you may deposit any data in the Oxford University Research Archive (ORA). This deposit licence does not apply to the deposit of any other work in ORA, including publications, for which you should read the <a href="/deposit_licence">ORA deposit licence</a>. A list of defined terms is included at the end of these deposit conditions.</p>
