        <dt>Person</dt>
        <dd>means any individual or organisation.</dd>
        <dt>Third party</dt>
        <dd>means any person other than you or the University.</dd>
        <dt>Work</dt>
        <dd>means any material other than data (in any format) that the University may permit or require you to deposit in ORA from time to time.</dd>
